{
  "stem": "26728.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He said, they're all-- they're all quarantined.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I said, well, we're going to get sprayed anyway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What the hell difference does it make, with the DDT.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so we went in one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And honest to God, I couldn't go any further than from here to you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I had to get out of there, because it was much-- it was much worse than the one in Buchenwald, in the same sense that these people were dying or dead and nobody was paying any attention to them.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean, there-- there was no medics around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they had already evidently been in there and said, just forget this place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We've got to help these other guys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "These guys are goners.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "These guys maybe have a chance, so they just forgot about them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So we got-- we walked back toward the gate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I see this little old guy sitting up against a barracks in the sun.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And this is April now, don't forget.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It had snowed the day before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The night before.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And one of the things that was so weird about the train and the corpses in the train that was on-- in the open, was they were dusted with snow.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The ground had-- it wasn't thick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was just kind of a dusting, but it gave it the damnedest appearance.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Kind of like Dickens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It reminded me of a Dickens Christmas tale, of the ghosts from the past or something like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was just, just weird.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I'm going back to the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I shouldn't have done-- OK, so this little guy is sitting there, and he has on a little hat, a little cap with no-- no bill, but it's a striped cap.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And it's just a little square like, like a little square cap.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
